  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK749">
<l>muṉaimukattu māṟṟalar cāya viṉaimukattu</l>
<l>vīṟeyti māṇṭa taraṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A fort is that which derives excellence from the stratagems made (by its inmates) to defeat their enemies in the battlefield.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
